Dawn.description:
Allows you to fulfill your |cffffffffVows|r.

Your next 10 damaging or healing abilities will trigger the |cffffffffFulfillment|r effect of your |CffffffffVow|r. Can only occur once per sec. Lasts 1 min.

@ext:|cFFFF9800Solar Power|r cannot be generated while |cffffffffDawn|r is active.:ext@

Vow of Dawn.description:
Direct ability damage or healing generates 1 |cFFFF9800Solar Power|r and bounces to 2 additional nearby targets with less value per target struck.

|cffffffffFulfillment|r: Doubles the amount of targets struck.

@ext:Only 1 |cffffffffVow|r can be active at a time.:ext@

Vow of Grace.description:
You generate 2 |cFFFF9800Solar Power|r every 2 sec and direct ability damage now regenerates 5% of your missing mana plus 10.

|cffffffffFulfillment|r: Halves the mana cost of all spells and abilities.

@ext:Only 1 |cffffffffVow|r can be active at a time.:ext@

Vow of Light.description:
Direct damage taken or direct healing taken by you generates 1 |cFFFF9800Solar Power|r and heals the nearest nearby ally equal to 20% of the amount.

|cffffffffFulfillment|r: Doubles the amount of healing done.

@ext:Only 1 |cffffffffVow|r can be active at a time.:ext@

Vow of Radiance.description:
Direct ability damage or healing generates 2 |cFFFF9800Solar Power|r and damages or heals for an additional 25% of the amount.

|cffffffffFulfillment|r: Doubles the damage or healing done.

@ext:Only 1 |cffffffffVow|r can be active at a time.:ext@

Vow of the Eclipse.description:
Direct ability damage or effective healing now generates 1 |cFFFF9800Solar Power|r and burns for 5% of the damage or healing done every 3 sec for 18 sec. Each trigger increases the damage of this effect. Additional applications do not refresh the duration.

|cffffffffFulfillment|r: Direct ability damage or healing done by you is increased by 10% on targets affected by |cFFFFFFFFVow of the Eclipse|r.

@ext:Only 1 |cffffffffVow|r can be active at a time.:ext@
